*   ^ In [Kentucky's&#160;2nd district](/Kentucky%27s_2nd_congressional_district), [Alexander D. Orr](/Alexander_D._Orr) was elected to the new seat.
*   ^ In [Kentucky's&#160;1st district](/Kentucky%27s_1st_congressional_district), [Christopher Greenup](/Christopher_Greenup) was elected to the new seat.
*   ^ In [Georgia's&#160;1st district](/Georgia%27s_1st_congressional_district), [John Milledge](/John_Milledge) was elected to the seat declared vacant because the previous election was contested.
*   ^ In [Maryland's&#160;2nd district](/Maryland%27s_2nd_congressional_district), [Joshua Seney](/Joshua_Seney) resigned to become a judge.
*   ^ In [Maryland's&#160;2nd district](/Maryland%27s_2nd_congressional_district), [William Hindman](/William_Hindman) was elected to fill the vacancy created when [Joshua Seney](/Joshua_Seney) resigned.
